				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${D}_{F}$$\end{document}DF, provides a qualitative threshold for magnetism. This picture is further supported by the observation of a second ferromagnetic metal phase near the second vHS in tWSe2 around \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
